### Chain Zod String Methods (TypeScript)

Source: https://github.com/colinhacks/zod/blob/main/packages/docs/content/packages/zod.mdx

This example illustrates the chainable API of Zod schemas, specifically showing how to apply multiple validation and transformation methods (min, max, toLowerCase) to a string type for concise schema definition.

```typescript
z.string()
  .min(5)
  .max(10)
  .toLowerCase();
```

