### Access Inner Array Element Schema in Zod

Source: https://github.com/colinhacks/zod/blob/main/packages/docs/content/api.mdx

Retrieves the schema of array elements in Zod using the unwrap method, returning the inner schema definition for inspection or further manipulation.

```typescript
stringArray.unwrap(); // => string schema
```

