### Unwrap inner schema from ZodOptional instance

Source: https://github.com/colinhacks/zod/blob/main/packages/docs/content/api.mdx

Demonstrates how to extract the original schema from a `ZodOptional` instance, showing the differences between Zod's `unwrap()` method and Zod Mini's `def.innerType` property.

```typescript
optionalYoda.unwrap(); // ZodLiteral<"yoda">
```

```typescript
optionalYoda.def.innerType; // ZodMiniLiteral<"yoda">
```

