### Make Zod Schema Nullable with `nullable` Method

Source: https://github.com/colinhacks/zod/blob/main/packages/docs-v3/README.md

Demonstrates how to make any Zod schema nullable using the `.nullable()` convenience method. This allows the schema to accept `null` in addition to its base type, providing an equivalent to `z.nullable(z.string())`.

```ts
const nullableString = z.string().nullable(); // string | null

// equivalent to
z.nullable(z.string());
```

