### Make All Properties Required in Zod Schema

Source: https://github.com/colinhacks/zod/blob/main/packages/docs/content/api.mdx

This illustrates how to convert all optional properties in a Zod object schema into required ones, mirroring TypeScript's `Required` utility type. It provides examples for both the direct schema method and a utility function approach.

```typescript
const RequiredRecipe = Recipe.required();
// { title: string; description: string; ingredients: string[] }
```

```typescript
const RequiredRecipe = z.required(Recipe);
// { title: string; description: string; ingredients: string[] }
```

